{"tid":685322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發] 澳門警方巳將涉嫌對香港遊客恐嚇勒索的士司機拘捕","createTime":"2018-05-31T10:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T13:28:55.000Z","uid":39539,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ccdf0c92c6f25e6392483bd7a73014f4a4db8eb0","tid":685322,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/182427_dd97ace655656de3847456ff70367595.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F182427_dd97ace655656de3847456ff70367595.gif&h=bab51c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(澳門電台消息) 1名 20多歲的士司機懷疑濫收車資，治安警根據網上流傳片段找到懷疑違規司機，有人承認是片段中的的士司機。<br />\n片段中顯示有乘客在葡京附近欲前往外港碼頭，被司機索取 200元車資。<br />\n治安警稱，事件中的的士司機去年 7月至今，涉及 12宗濫收車資和 1宗拒載。片段同時顯示他在雨天涉嫌沒有協助乘客搬運行李，以及沒有填寫行車日誌等違規行爲，已移交交通事務局跟進。<br />\n治安警又呼籲市民和旅客，舉報一旦遇到的的士違規行為，警方必定依法打擊有關。"},{"pid":"7d46c9e52562b5d8e69533234a20c852d66a4d76","tid":685322,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"澳門黑的無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要求無罪釋放<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8dc7cd42f89648b3be1cd8355af330568464c0","tid":685322,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"治安警又呼籲市民和旅客，舉報一旦遇到的的士違規行為，警方必定依法打擊有關。<br />\n係咪要笑,澳門完全唔會理"},{"pid":"c3a925086b2d98f554070ca4ac1c2f52ae26f0f9","tid":685322,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"收我附加費？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39151e2100a4482fe38fa73002b487bedc37a000","tid":685322